Two Pointers for Sorted Array (No Sliding Window)
---------------------------------------------------

(Used for problems like finding pairs with sum k, merging arrays, removing duplicates)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    int left = 0, right = n - 1;

    while (left < right) {
        // Evaluate some function or condition using nums[left] and nums[right]
    
        if (/* condition is satisfied */) {
            // Process or return result
        } else if (/* need to increase total */) {
            left++;
        } else {
            right--;s
        }
    }
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

